Maggi recipe from shiva kumar (shivactrl)

Step 1. Go to shop and buy 2 packets of maggi
step 2. Take a bowl and add 2 glass of water and switch on the gas.
step 3.Now add one full pack of maggi and one half from the other packet.{bcz two full packets  is too much and one is not enough (: }
step 4.After 2mins add the maggi masala and stir it properly
step 5.leave it for 4-5mins.
step 6.swittch off the gas and you're maggi is ready to eat.


Thank you.
